.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, teacher, chef, paramedic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, sports, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, lacrosse, snowboarding
 1. the dancer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 2. the teacher is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
 4. the paramedic is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
 5. the teacher is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 6. the person watching western movies is not the chef##6
 7. the dancer is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
 8. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is not to the right of the dancer##8
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the chef##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Job         | chef       | dancer | teacher  | paramedic    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports       | western    | scientific | fantasy    |
| Sport         | snowboarding | baseball   | lacrosse   | basketball |

