.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, musical, scientific, spy
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, engineer, fisherman, security-guard
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, taxi, train, tram
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the fisherman##1
 2. the chef is not the person watching spy movies##6
 3. the chef is between the fisherman and the person driving the train##2
 4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the train is not the security-guard##6
 8. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the security-guard##8
 9. the security-guard is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
10. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
11. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the security-guard##8
12. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
13. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | adventure | spy        | scientific |
| Job   | fisherman | chef   | engineer | security-guard     |
| Transport     | tram      | taxi      | train      | car        |

