.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, march, april
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indonesian, malaysian, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, ship, subway
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
 2. the pakistani is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the malaysian##7
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the german is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
 7. the pakistani is on the left or right of the german##3
 8. the german is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
10. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##8
11. the german is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
12. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
13. the german is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
14. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Birthday         | july    | march | april | may    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | pakistani    | german      | indonesian |
| Transport     | helicopter | car          | subway      | ship       |

