4 different games are played: chess, snooker, monopoly, scrabble
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, japanese, nigerian
 1. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
 2. the brazilian is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the brazilian is between the person playing snooker and the nigerian##2
 4. the british is not to the left of the japanese##8
 5. the person playing chess is not to the right of the person eating carrot##8
 6. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
 7. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
 8. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8
 9. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the british##5
10. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the nigerian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | watermelon | tomato    | plum     | carrot    |
| Game   | snooker      | scrabble    | monopoly      | chess |
| Nationality   | japanese   | brazilian | nigerian | british   |

