There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, italian, pakistani, thai
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, subway, taxi, tram
 1. the thai is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5
 2. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the thai##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the chinese##3
 4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the thai##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the boat is not the alhambra-smoker##6
 9. the davidoff-smoker is not to the left of the chinese##8
10. the chinese is not to the right of the alhambra-smoker##8
11. the siglo-smoker is somewhere between the chinese and the person driving the boat##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4    |
| Cigar           | bongani  | siglo | alhambra | davidoff |
| Nationality   | pakistani | thai           | chinese  | italian |
| Transport     | boat      | taxi           | tram     | subway  |

