 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is not the townhouse house##6
 4. the cottage house is between the person driving the scooter and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
 5. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the townhouse house##8
 6. the tower house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
 7. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
 8. the townhouse house is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the tower house is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
10. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
11. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
12. the person driving the taxi is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
13. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the townhouse house##1
14. the person driving the snowmobile is not the tower house##6

