5. the colombian is not the coach##6
6. the owner of the snake is on the left of the russian##1
7. the coach is somewhere between the dancer and the chef##7
8. the dancer is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
9. the coach is the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | colombian | canadian     | russian  | indonesian |
| Pet           | fish      | snake        | rabbit   | chinchilla |
| Job         | chef  | coach | dancer | librarian       |

 